caption:
🗣️ Does your son support Real Madrid?

🗣️ Szczesny: “Yes, before I came here he was. But after watching Barca’s games slowly started to understand Yamal is not bad Lewandowski is not bad Pedri is not bad. 

When we played Super final he was supporting Barca, ​​so maybe he’s starting to convert. He has no choice!”

The verbal agreement between Wojciech Szczesny and Barça over new contract is almost done! He has had an incredible season! 🔥

🏟️ 18 Games
💯 UNDEFEATED with Him in Goal
⛔ 10 Clean Sheets
🔥 2 Finals
🏆 1 Trophy
